output.name: Iron Forge Nest
output.description: Iron Forge Nest is dedicated to harnessing the transformative power of AI through its project management platform, ScatterShotAI. Founded in 2023, this innovative company aims to empower teams by enabling seamless collaboration between humans and AI, ensuring that project execution aligns with strategic goals. With a focus on AI safety and transparency, Iron Forge Nest is poised to lead the revolution in high-growth SaaS solutions, helping organizations optimize their project workflows and enhance human potential. Located in Seattle, the company actively seeks visionary leaders to join their mission.
